</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term><listitem><simpara> 0 on success or a negative value if an error occurs.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
